<h2>
    Key Chinook Salmon Runs Near Salem
</h2>
<h3>
    Spring Chinook Run
</h3>
<p>
    The spring Chinook salmon start their journey upriver as early as March and are typically available through June. These fish are prized for their firm texture and mild flavor, making them a top culinary choice.
</p>
<h3>
    Fall Chinook Run
</h3>
<p>
    Fall Chinook are generally larger and start their run from August through October. They are more abundant and are considered more aggressive, which often translates to higher catch rates during this season.
</p>
